# =============================================================================
# Stochastic Transit Router - Git Ignore Configuration
# Files and Directories Excluded from Version Control
#
# This file specifies which files and directories should NOT be committed to
# the Git repository. These typically include:
# - Build artifacts and compiled files
# - Virtual environments and dependencies
# - IDE and editor configuration
# - Testing and coverage reports
# - Cache and temporary files
# - Secrets and sensitive data
# - Large data files and generated outputs
#
# Documentation: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore
# =============================================================================

